experience.description: Analyzed paper consumption statistics across all departments and processes, identifying usage patterns and inefficiencies.\nLed the development of a Salesforce Tableau dashboard, effectively summarizing key results and insights from the analysis.\nIdentified cost-saving opportunities, contributing to more efficient resource utilization.

Developed a living space co-ownership application to facilitate shared arrangements, enhancing user experience and functionality.\nBuilt the application using React, Next.js, Prisma ORM, MySQL, and Auth0, ensuring a robust and secure platform.
